linuxcnc-ethercat (0.9.5) unstable; urgency=medium

  * - allow string modparam value
  * - add support for named stdios for EL6900
  * - removed unused PDO mappings for EL6900
  * - removed EL6900 debug pins for fsoe data
  * - optional preinit function per device to allow dynamic configuration (i.e. PDO mapping count) - FSOE parameters per device
  * - fixed string modparam parsing
  * - fixed EL6900 dynamic stdio mapping
  * - added initial ax5805 support
  * - fixed fsoe example for dynamic stdio mapping
  * - moved fsoeConf initialization to slave preinit function
  * - removed obsolete comment
  * - added ax5100 support - created class for ax5xxx
  * - added AX51xx support to AX5805
  * - autodetect number of ax5805 channels
  * - move fsoe config for AX5805 to AX5nxx driver
  * Add support for Beckhoff EL30x4 (4-port 12-bit analog in) and EL3202 (2-port temperature in) modules.
  * Added semi-functioning support for EL3403 3-phase power meter.  Still returns bogus results, but mine don't have power applied at the moment, so it *might* not be a bug.
  * Minor EL3403 cleanups; now reads all-0 instead of -INT_MAX.
  * Addition of a driver for EM37xx-series pressure sensors.
  * Add product codes for EL3004, EL3044, and EL3054 to EL30x4 code.
  * Replace my EL3403 module with A.Chimeno's from the LinuxCNC forum.
  * Fix phantom sync error on 0x6000:0e.
  * Add EP2308 support (still somewhat broken) and add IDs for EP10[01]8 devices.
  * Initial driver for EP23xx combo in/out digial I/O boxes.
  * Add support (untested) for EP2316 devices.
  * Rename the EL7041 driver from el7041_1000 to simply el7041.
  * Adding Card Definitions
  * removed redundant changelog
  * added support for EL1918 as TwinSAFE plc
  * Support added for EL9576
  * Support added for EL9576
  * Added support for EL9576
  * Support added for EL9576
  * Removing Conflicts
  * Adding EP2349
  * Add Delta MS300 initial
  * ms300 initial, el6900 pdo fix
  * fixed merge comment
  * removed txpdo state bit from el6900, due firmware change
  * add additional AX5100 Types
  * Add Delta MS300 initial
  * fixed el1918 to adapt new el6900 config method
  * added inverted inputs to EL1904
  * clean up EL6900
  * fixed el1918_logic pdo count calculation
  * better buffer handling of dynamic fsoe data
  * allow dynamic pdo mapping via params for ax5
  * fixed dynamic pdo mapping index update
  * added ax5 diagonistic number pin
  * removed unused raw feedback pins
  * fixed enc subclass initialization
  * fixed PDO count calculation
  * changed ramp scaling
  * fix bug PDO Mapping MS300
  * fix ms300 pdo count bug
  * Ethercat Float Test
  * added delta MS300 velo scale parameter
  * Update for README.md of linuxcnc-ethercat/linuxcnc-ethercat.
  * Create CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
  * Create CONTRIBUTING
  * Create c-cpp.yml
  * Update c-cpp.yml
  * Update c-cpp.yml
  * fixed typo
  * added el5002 and el5032
  * Add support for Beckhoff EL1804
  * Fully implemented EP2316
  * Removed old #defines
  * Renamed diag pins
  * Add EP2308, EP2318 and EP2328
  * Add missing chnages to lcec_conf
  * Add missing changes to lcec_main
  * testing
  * Simplifying CI dependencies
  * Break the CI action up into multiple workflows, with Ethercat Master and LinuxCNC itself being cached between runs.
  * Update CONTRIBUTING and add clang-format default
  * add el6090
  * initial per-device documentation
  * Add script to fetch and decode ESI files from Beckhoff and Omron.
  * Create device docs from ESI files
